# Medical
<Box>
Isn’t it a bit unnerving that doctors call what they do “practice”?
― George Carlin
</Box>

To practice medicine in SS14 is to diagnose patients, treat injuries, treat diseases, and revive the dead.  As such, it is your job to ensure that the crew remains alive and healthy so that they can keep the station functioning.

The medical field requires a multitude of tools; for your convenience, see the glossary of medical equipment below.

